%N A394253 Decimal expansion of Product_{p prime} (1 + (p-1)/(p^2*(p+1))).
%C A394253 The asymptotic mean of the number of common unitary divisors of two positive integers selected independently at random.
%F A394253 Equals lim_{m->oo} (1/m^2) * Sum_{i,j=1..m} A034444(gcud(i, j)), where gcud is the greatest common unitary divisor function.
%F A394253 Equals zeta(2) * Proudct_{p prime} (1 - 2/p^3 + 1/p^4).
%e A394253 1.224974993934192376418974014138158800346682537481536...
%o A394253 (PARI) prodeulerrat(1 + (p-1)/(p^2*(p+1)))
